cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

The paper focuses on few-shot learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed benchmark involves evaluating models on images from diverse domains, which could also fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) if the images include text. Additionally, the use of ensemble learning and transfer learning could also relate to multimedia (cs.MM) if the models are trained on different types of data such as audio or video.
